to.networld.soap.security.interfaces
Interface ISecSOAPMessage

All Known Implementing Classes:
SecSOAPMessage
public interface ISecSOAPMessage

Interface that wraps the message with a security layer and useful methods to handle security related features.

To gain a concrete object call SOAPSecMessageFactory.newInstance(int)

Author:
Alex Oberhauser
